column16: Jose Iglesias doubles (1) on a ground ball to left fielder Vernon Wells.   Jackie Bradley to 3rd.
Jackie Bradley singles on a ground ball to center fielder Brett Gardner.   Shane Victorino scores.
Shane Victorino singles on a line drive to left fielder Vernon Wells.   Jarrod Saltalamacchia scores.
Jarrod Saltalamacchia singles on a ground ball to right fielder Ichiro Suzuki.
Mike Napoli grounds out, second baseman Robinson Cano to first baseman Lyle Overbay.
New York Yankees pitcher Hiroki Kuroda left the game due to an injured hand.
Dustin Pedroia grounds out, shortstop Eduardo Nunez to first baseman Lyle Overbay.
